<paragraph id="8BA6624CFF9FAC4947DFFF6B9F3BC8E6" blockId="16.[189,346,175,199]" box="[189,346,175,199]" pageId="16" pageNumber="149">
<emphasis id="B96DBE5EFF9FAC4947DFFF6B9F3BC8E6" bold="true" box="[189,346,175,199]" pageId="16" pageNumber="149">Comparazioni:</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BA6624CFF9FAC4947DFFF129D5CC968" blockId="16.[189,1179,213,329]" pageId="16" pageNumber="149">
La nuova specie presenta la porzione prossimale della spermateca avvolta a spire come in 
<taxonomicName id="4C1919CFFF9FAC4947DFFF309FDAC92D" authority="PACE, 1997" authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="1997" box="[189,443,244,268]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Apalonia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="149" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bondensis">
<emphasis id="B96DBE5EFF9FAC4947DFFF309F56C92D" box="[189,311,244,268]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="149">A. bondensis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF881FBDFF9FAC494622FF309FDAC92D" author="PACE, R." box="[320,443,244,268]" pageId="16" pageNumber="149" pagination="17 - 48" refId="ref12052" refString="PACE, R. 1997: Aleocharinae della Colombia e dell'Ecuador. Parte III (conclusione). (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae). - Revue suisse de Zoologie 104: 17 - 48." type="journal article" year="1997">PACE, 1997</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, della 
<collectingCountry id="F30E22DCFF9FAC494563FF309C0AC92D" box="[513,619,244,268]" name="Colombia" pageId="16" pageNumber="149">Colombia</collectingCountry>
, ma in essa le spire sono ampie e di numero ridotto, mentre in 
<taxonomicName id="4C1919CFFF9FAC49464EFED79FE8C90A" authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="1997" box="[300,393,275,299]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Apalonia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="149" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bondensis">
<emphasis id="B96DBE5EFF9FAC49464EFED79FE8C90A" box="[300,393,275,299]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="149">bondensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sono strette e numerose. Il pronoto, inoltre, è meno trasverso di quello di 
<taxonomicName id="4C1919CFFF9FAC4947DFFEF59F7BC968" authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="1997" box="[189,282,305,329]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Apalonia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="149" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bondensis">
<emphasis id="B96DBE5EFF9FAC4947DFFEF59F7BC968" box="[189,282,305,329]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="149">bondensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
e giallo-rossiccio, mentre in 
<taxonomicName id="4C1919CFFF9FAC494520FEF59CFEC968" authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="1997" box="[578,671,305,329]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Apalonia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="149" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bondensis">
<emphasis id="B96DBE5EFF9FAC494520FEF59CFEC968" box="[578,671,305,329]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="149">bondensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
è giallo-bruno.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BA6624CFF9FAC4947DFFEA19FFEC9BA" blockId="16.[189,1179,357,411]" pageId="16" pageNumber="149">
<emphasis id="B96DBE5EFF9FAC4947DFFEA19F56C95C" bold="true" box="[189,311,357,381]" pageId="16" pageNumber="149">Etimologia:</emphasis>
La nuova specie è chiamata «macchia sulla fronte» per la presenza di questo suo carattere differenziale.
</paragraph>
